        "title": "Gilead Sciences’s (NASDAQ:GILD) Q1 CY2026: Beats On Revenue",
        "description": "",
        "summary": "Biopharmaceutical company Gilead Sciences (NASDAQ:GILD) reported Q1 CY2026 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 4.4% year on year to $6.96 billion. The company expects the full year’s revenue to be around $30.2 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.03 per share was 6.3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
